System Architecture 

The backend follows a layered architecture:
Layer 1 — Client Layer
React Native Mobile App
Web Client
Responsibilities:
User Interface
Authentication Screens
Journaling
Daily Pulse
AI Chat
Layer 2 — Orchestration Layer
Node.js acts as the central coordinator.
Responsibilities:
Authentication
Consent Management
Session Management
RBAC
Safety Middleware
API Routing
Layer 3 — Service Layer
External services integrated with Node.js:
Supabase
FastAPI
Firebase
LiveKit
Redis
Layer 4 — Intelligence Layer
AI-specific processing:
Emotion Classification
Memory Retrieval
Safety Engine
Model Routing
Layer 5 — Gateway Layer
External integrations:
OpenRouter
Razorpay
Layer 6 — Foundation Models
GPT-4o
Claude Sonnet
Gemini
Whisper


